      "name": "Product Info",
      "settings": {
        "width": "page",
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/Square.png",
        "header_type": "left",
        "heading": "<h2>73 layers of Damascus. Powder steel core.</h2>",
        "content": "<p>The Master Series 2 combines Xinzuo's flagship 14Cr14MoVNb powder steel — the same core found in the acclaimed Lan Series — with 73 layers of Damascus cladding. At 62 HRC, this is a blade built for serious edge retention and precision cutting.</p>",
        "icon_block_state": true,
        "first_num": "3",
        "second_num": "3",
        "color_scheme": "scheme-5",
        "padding_top": 80,
        "padding_bottom": 80
      }
    },
    "product_info2_8biKrj": {
      "type": "product-info2",
      "name": "Product Info2",
      "settings": {
        "width": "page",
        "heading_title": "FLAGSHIP STEEL. MASTER CRAFTSMANSHIP.",
        "heading_content": "<h2>Where Powder Steel Meets Master Design</h2>",
        "header_type": "left",
        "background_type": "none",
        "block_type": "text",
        "heading_footer": "The Master Series 2 is the pinnacle of Hezhen's Damascus range — combining the same powder steel technology found in Xinzuo's flagship Lan Series with Hezhen's Master-grade craftsmanship. The result is a blade that performs at the highest level while wearing the Master designation.",
        "image_video": "image",
        "color_scheme": "scheme-5",
        "footer_state": "visible",
        "footer_type": "first",
        "footer_left": "<h2>THE POWDER STEEL ADVANTAGE</h2>",
        "footer_right": "<p>14Cr14MoVNb powder steel is produced through a process that creates an ultra-fine, uniform grain structure. This means better edge retention, improved toughness, and a blade that responds beautifully to precision sharpening. At 62 HRC, it significantly outperforms standard 60 HRC Damascus.</p>",
        "padding_top": 80,
        "padding_bottom": 80,
        "additional_footer": false,
        "additional_content1": "",
        "additional_content2": ""
      }
    },
    "product_info2_eVwTgB": {
      "type": "product-info2",
      "name": "Product Info2",
      "settings": {
        "width": "full",
        "heading_title": "Handle Design",
        "heading_content": "<h2>Rosewood<br/>Master Craftsmanship</h2>",
        "header_type": "center",
        "background_type": "none",
        "block_type": "text",
        "heading_footer": "",
        "image_video": "image",
        "color_scheme": "scheme-5",
        "footer_state": "visible",
        "footer_type": "second",
        "footer_left": "<p>The Master Series 2 pairs its flagship steel with a classic rosewood handle — warm, dense, and naturally oil-rich. The Hezhen Master designation ensures the highest standard of handle fitting and finish. Every joint, every curve is refined to match the precision of the blade.</p>",
        "footer_right": "<h2>Warm</h2><p>Rosewood's natural warmth and rich grain make every handle unique.</p><h2>Dense</h2><p>Naturally oil-rich and resistant to moisture and wear over time.</p><h2>Refined</h2><p>Master-grade fitting ensures seamless joints and a premium feel.</p>",
        "padding_top": 80,
        "padding_bottom": 80,
        "additional_footer": false,
        "additional_content1": "",
        "additional_content2": ""
      }
    },
    "product_info2_GjRq8Y": {
      "type": "product-info2",
      "name": "Product Info2",
      "settings": {
        "width": "page",
        "heading_title": "",
        "heading_content": "<h2>Why Choose the<br/>Master Series 2</h2>",
        "header_type": "center",
        "background_type": "none",
        "block_type": "text",
        "heading_footer": "",
        "image_video": "image",
        "color_scheme": "scheme-5",
        "footer_state": "visible",
        "footer_type": "third",
        "footer_left": "<p>This is the upgrade path for anyone who loves the Master Series design but wants the best steel Xinzuo offers. The jump from 60 HRC to 62 HRC means noticeably longer edge retention between sharpenings. Combined with 73-layer Damascus, it's the most refined Master Series blade.</p>",
        "footer_right": "<p>With 8 carefully selected knife types, the Master Series 2 focuses on the essential blades that benefit most from powder steel precision. The Hezhen Master designation guarantees premium materials and construction at every level.</p>",
        "padding_top": 80,
        "padding_bottom": 80,
        "additional_footer": false,
        "additional_content1": "",
        "additional_content2": ""
      }
    },
